column5: Woah...What kind of camera is this

Waiting for one to be called,”Wingardium Leviosa!”

People handle situations differently, no disrespect, but that’s like saying “Don’t whine about something you struggle with because others have it worse” others also have it better.  Others have low functioning autism, others don’t have autism at all and can’t walk or think on their own. We all have our struggles, so we should all have the right to say something about them.
